Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.11,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:03.16,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Zoro-dono! Zoro-dono! Estamos aqui!
